Detailed Description

Datapath error interrupt enable Bits. This register is used to independently enable each event to trigger the ErrIrq interrupt line. Only events whose corresponding enable bit is set to 1 can trigger the interrupt line. Hard reset is 0x0000000, i.e. all interrupt lines are disabled
